author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Mondo TV France sells non exclusive online rights to Sherlock Yack to Netflix
text:
Oct 23 Mondo TV France SA :
* Signs non exclusive license agreement with Netflix for the online distribution of Sherlock Yack in Italy, Spain and Portugal
Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
